        <td>
        	<%=link_to("App Login Flow", :action => :oauth_app_login)%>
        </td>
        <td>
          <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-oauth-v2-20#section-4.4">Client Credentials</a>
        </td>
        <td>
          Use this flow if your application needs to take various administrative actions, such as retrieving statistics data. The calls will not be made on behalf of the user, but on behalf of the app itself. 
        </td>
      </tr -->
  	</table>
  </p>
      
</div>

<%= render :partial => "footer" %>
